  "body": "<p>Our focus this month at Two Peas in a Bucket was on \"The Little Things\". This is how my project came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1a-DSC_1017-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3dd07891abb9e15c.jpg?v=1782532027\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1b-DSC_1018-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c2542a81cb2dd104.jpg?v=1782532030\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1c-DSC_1019-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bb8ef42c9244436c.jpg?v=1782532033\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1d-.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/046bc9a63689203f.jpg?v=1782532035\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1e-DSC_1021-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bbd3950c57d8cc14.jpg?v=1782532038\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1f-thesmallestthings.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5b1344b63d3a2719.jpg?v=1782532041\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Sometimes | Copyright Two Peas in a Bucket - where you can also see the full supply list.And I am super excited about these brand new, exclusive stamp sets for Two Peas - especially this one called <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/two-peas/143568-nailed-it-shimelle-laine-4x6-clear-stamp/\">Nailed It by shimelle</a>, telling it like it is...and this one called, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/two-peas/143567-you-are-here-4x6-clear-stamp/\">You Are Here</a>.</p>"
